<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1 class="mb-4">About Fitness Tracker</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h2>Project Overview</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        Fitness Tracker is a web application designed to help users track their workouts, monitor nutritional
        intake, and track progress toward their fitness goals.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h2 class="mb-3">Data Sources</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-0">ExerciseDB API</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p>Exercise data is sourced from the ExerciseDB API, which provides comprehensive information about various exercises including:</p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">Exercise name</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Exercise type (strength, cardio, flexibility, etc.)</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Target muscle group</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Required equipment</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Difficulty level</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Instructions</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Demo image/GIF URL</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <small class="text-muted">Source: <a href="https://rapidapi.com/justin-WFnsXH_t6/api/exercisedb" target="_blank">ExerciseDB API</a></small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-0">Foundation Foods CSV</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p>Nutritional information is imported from the USDA Foundation Foods dataset, which includes:</p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">Food item name</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Calorie content per serving</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Protein content (grams)</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Carbohydrate content (grams)</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Fat content (grams)</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Serving size information</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Food category</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <small class="text-muted">Source: <a href="https://fdc.nal.usda.gov/download-datasets.html" target="_blank">USDA FoodData Central</a></small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-0">Faker Gem</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p>Generated user and workout data including:</p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">User profiles (name, age, height, weight, fitness level)</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Workout logs (date, duration, exercises performed)</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">User fitness goals and progress tracking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h2 class="mb-3">Database Structure</h2>
      <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="table table-striped table-hover">
          <thead class="table-dark">
            <tr>
              <th>Table</th>
              <th>Description</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>users</strong></td>
              <td>User profiles and details</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>exercises</strong></td>
              <td>Exercise information and instructions</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>workouts</strong></td>
              <td>Workout plans and logs</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>workout_exercises</strong></td>
              <td>Join table connecting workouts and exercises</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>foods</strong></td>
              <td>Nutritional information for food items</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>food_categories</strong></td>
              <td>Categories for organizing food items</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>meal_logs</strong></td>
              <td>User's food consumption records</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>meal_foods</strong></td>
              <td>Join table connecting meals and foods</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>progress_entries</strong></td>
              <td>User's progress tracking data</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 text-center mb-5">
      <h3>Entity Relationship Diagram</h3>
      <img src="<%= asset_path('fitness_tracker_erd.jpeg') %>" alt="Fitness Tracker ERD" class="img-fluid border">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>